        <div n="912-62GI" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-line-1"><hi rend="display-initial">Y</hi>OUR house of hair and lady's hand,</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-line-2"> At first did put me to a stand.</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-line-3"> I have it now,──'tis plain enough,</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-line-4"> Your hairy business is a <hi rend="underline">Muff</hi>.</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-line-5"> Your engine fraught with cooling gales,</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-line-6"> At once so like your mast and sails,<gap/><gap/></l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-line-7"> And for the rhime to <hi rend="underline">you're the man</hi>,</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-912-62GI-line-8"> What fits it better than a <hi rend="underline">fan</hi>?912-62GI   </l></lg></div>
